      <title>台湾抗议、立法者冲突考验黎智英的领导能力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/taiwan-protests-lawmaker-clashes-show-test-to-lai-s-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾朝野政党之间掀起新一轮政治角力，引发街头抗议和议员争斗，这加剧了人们对赖清德总统是否有能力治理全球最危险的地缘政治热点地区之一的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/taiwan-protests-lawmaker-clashes-show-test-to-lai-s-leadership</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 02:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯准备再次大幅加息以对抗通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/russia-braces-for-another-steep-rate-hike-in-battle-on-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯准备在周五再次大幅加息，因为该央行在控制近期远高于预期的通胀方面仍未取得任何成功。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/russia-braces-for-another-steep-rate-hike-in-battle-on-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 02:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普支持的共和党拨款计划在众议院失败，政府停摆临近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/trump-backed-gop-funding-plan-fails-in-house-as-shutdown-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，距离美国政府关门仅剩 24 个多小时，共和党控制的众议院否决了当选总统唐纳德·特朗普支持的一项临时拨款计划，这标志着华盛顿为期两天的特别会议圆满结束，这也考验了新任总统权力的极限。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/trump-backed-gop-funding-plan-fails-in-house-as-shutdown-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 23:58:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登将在总统任期内最后一次拜访教皇方济各</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/biden-to-visit-pope-francis-one-last-time-during-presidency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将于下个月访问罗马和梵蒂冈，这可能是他最后一次出访海外，他希望巩固自己在世界舞台上的地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/biden-to-visit-pope-francis-one-last-time-during-presidency</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 23:57:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本央行寻求更多数据 能源价格上涨导致日本通胀加速</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/japan-s-inflation-picks-up-as-boj-seeks-more-data-for-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行在决定下次加息时间前继续分析数据，随着政府能源补贴影响的减弱，日本关键通胀指标走强。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/japan-s-inflation-picks-up-as-boj-seeks-more-data-for-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 23:35:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>神秘目击事件发生后，五角大楼向新泽西州派遣反无人机技术人员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/pentagon-sends-anti-drone-tech-as-worry-over-sightings-persists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼已经向新泽西州一个地区运送了反无人机技术，该地区曾出现过神秘飞机，令当地居民感到紧张，并有人指责联邦政府没有认真对待这些事件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/pentagon-sends-anti-drone-tech-as-worry-over-sightings-persists</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 22:58:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“唯一的赢家是中国”：安大略省省长向特朗普提出贸易恳求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/ontario-premier-doug-ford-says-china-would-win-trade-war-in-plea-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大最大省级经济体的领导人希望直接向特朗普政府提出反对关税的论点——如果北美国家卷入贸易战，中国将是主要受益者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/ontario-premier-doug-ford-says-china-would-win-trade-war-in-plea-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 22:30:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西国会进一步削弱卢拉的削减支出计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/brazil-congress-further-dilutes-lula-s-spending-cut-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西众议院在三天内第三次削弱了旨在缓解投资者对该国财政状况恶化的担忧的支出削减方案的关键条款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/brazil-congress-further-dilutes-lula-s-spending-cut-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 20:50:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默任命贸易资深人士曼德尔森为英国驻美国大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/starmer-taps-trade-veteran-mandelson-as-uk-s-ambassador-to-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 将任命资深工党人物和贸易专家彼得·曼德尔森 (Peter Mandelson) 为英国驻美国大使，以避免英国受到唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 征收关税的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/starmer-taps-trade-veteran-mandelson-as-uk-s-ambassador-to-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 20:05:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果特朗普驱逐墨西哥人，Sheinbaum 准备接收他们</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/sheinbaum-is-ready-to-receive-mexicans-if-trump-deports-them</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果当选总统唐纳德·特朗普履行驱逐出境的承诺，墨西哥准备接收居住在美国的本国公民，但不会成为其他国籍移民的“安全第三国”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/sheinbaum-is-ready-to-receive-mexicans-if-trump-deports-them</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 18:48:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
